  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Welcome to Hugsville!\n\nWelcome to Hugsville! Build-A-Bear Workshop mascots Bearemy and Pawlette Coufur guide you throughout this open-ended adventure. Explore the world, decorate your home, play games, or chat with friends!\n\nFeatures:\n\n• 13 playable furry friends to choose from and customize\n• Go on quests, build and create, play local wireless mini-games with your furry friends, and more!\n• 5 different \"Fun Zones\" featuring mini-games, including the Beach, Forest, Jungle, Desert and Icecap.\n• Collect items to unlock new gameplay and rewards.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ]
